title: US Accepted Iran’s Bid to Maintain Uranium Enrichment, ISNA Says
description: US officials have accepted Iran’s red line of continuing to enrich uranium, the semi-official Iranian Students’ News Agency quoted one of the country’s diplomats as saying.
